snippet.textDisplay: Gaan tu bhalei lagise but Moran jonojati r gaan gaise hati hikua gaan jihetu you’ll should have shown the moran culture… aanki moran gamusa ekhon u lua nai and and this is our old traditional song for elephant training but in here moran jonojatir eku atau dekhua nai plus gaan tu beleg kori dile ekebare and hindi u mix korise not what I expected bout this song, vabisilu bhal dore moran r porompora u dekhaise but nah.. and they made it like modern bihu but nor this is a bihu song or a modern song it’s our old traditional song.
